    <string name="tutorial_got_it">Got it!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_welcome_title">Welcome to Tap Empire!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_welcome_body">Tap the coin to earn money!\n\n💰 Each tap gives you coins\n🏭 Buy businesses to earn automatically\n⬆️ Upgrade to boost your production\n🌍 Unlock new worlds as you progress\n\nStart tapping and build your empire!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_generators_title">Your First Business!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_generators_body">Great! You bought your first business.\n\n🏭 Businesses produce coins automatically\n⬆️ Buy more to increase production\n💡 Each business has unique upgrades\n\nKeep growing your portfolio!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_prestige_title">Prestige Available!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_prestige_body">You can now perform a Prestige!\n\n⭐ Reset your progress for permanent multipliers\n📈 Each prestige makes you stronger\n🔄 Your coins and businesses reset, but you keep prestige bonuses\n\nGo to More → Prestige when ready!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_minigames_title">Mini-Games Unlocked!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_minigames_body">You\'ve unlocked mini-games!\n\n🎮 Play games to earn bonus rewards\n⏱️ Each game has a cooldown between plays\n🏆 Better performance = bigger rewards\n\nCheck them out in the Games tab!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_pets_title">Pets!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_pets_body">You got your first pet!\n\n🐾 Pets give production bonuses\n❤️ Feed, play with, and care for them\n💊 Watch out for diseases\n🏠 Visit the nursery to manage your pets\n\nA happy pet means more coins!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_worlds_title">New World!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_worlds_body">You\'ve traveled to a new world!\n\n🌍 Each world has unique businesses\n✨ Different themes and bonuses\n💰 Higher worlds = bigger earnings\n\nExplore and conquer all worlds!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_workers_title">Workers Unlocked!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_workers_body">You\'ve unlocked the Worker System!\n\n👷 Hire workers from random boxes\n📋 Create contracts to negotiate terms\n🤝 Workers must accept your offer\n🎓 Each worker has unique education &amp; skills\n📍 Assign them to businesses to boost production\n✊ Keep them happy or they\'ll go on strike!\n\nGo to More → Workers to start hiring!</string>

